---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Container from '@components/container.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Infinite Limit, LLC">
  <Container>
    <section class="py-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy for Infinite Limit, LLC</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 4, 2025</p>

      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-6">
        At Infinite Limit, LLC, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. 
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and safeguard your data when you interact with our 
        website, particularly through our contact form. By using our website, you consent to the practices described 
        in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with any part of this policy, please refrain from using our website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-2">
        1.1. <strong>Personal Information</strong>: When you submit our contact form, we collect personal information you provide, including your name, email address, and the message content.
      </p>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        1.2. <strong>Usage Data</strong>: We do not collect usage data, tracking information, or cookies beyond what is necessary to process your contact form submission. Our only data collection occurs through the voluntary information you provide in the form.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-2">
        2.1. We use the information collected solely to respond to your inquiries or messages submitted via our contact form.
      </p>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-2">
        2.2. Your personal information may be used to communicate with you regarding your specific inquiry or follow-up related to your message.
      </p>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        2.3. We do not use your data for marketing, analytics, or any other purposes beyond fulfilling your request.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-2">
        3.1. Infinite Limit, LLC will not sell, rent, or lease your personal information to third parties.
      </p>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-2">
        3.2. We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website, such as Web3Forms, which processes your contact form submission to deliver it to our email. These providers are bound by confidentiality and data protection obligations. We recommend reviewing <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Web3Forms’ privacy policy</a> for details on their practices.
      </p>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        3.3. We may disclose your information if required by law, or when we believe such action is necessary to protect our rights, comply with legal proceedings, or enforce our policies.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">4. Data Security</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-2">
        4.1. Infinite Limit, LLC implements reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, loss, misuse, or alteration. Our contact form data is handled securely by Web3Forms, and once received, we protect it using standard security practices, such as password-protected email accounts and secure storage.
      </p>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        4.2. While we take appropriate precautions, no method of data transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security of your information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">5. Third-Party Links and Services</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        5.1. Our website may contain links to third-party websites or services, such as Web3Forms. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third parties. Please review their privacy policies before interacting with them.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        6.1. Our website is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such information, please contact us immediately, and we will promptly delete it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">7. Your Choices and Rights</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        7.1. You have the right to request the deletion of your personal information, such as a submitted message, after we have responded to your inquiry. To make such a request, please contact us at <a href="mailto:p.oflaherty@infinitelimit.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">p.oflaherty@infinitelimit.com</a>. We will comply with your request to the extent permitted by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        8.1. We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices, legal requirements, or other factors. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the “Last Updated” date will be revised accordingly. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="block text-justify text-gray-600 mb-4">
        9.1. If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal information, please contact us at:  
        <a href="mailto:p.oflaherty@infinitelimit.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">p.oflaherty@infinitelimit.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </Container>
</Layout>